Package: wa.gov
Title: Washington State Open Data Client
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sean", "B", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@scrapeable.com")
Description: Self-contained client for Washington State open data (data.wa.gov). Covers political finance, health providers, data breaches, wildlife, labor, cannabis/liquor licensing, education, environment, criminal justice, and government contracts via the Socrata SODA API.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Depends: R (>= 4.1.0)
Imports:
    httr2,
    jsonlite,
    dplyr,
    tibble
